---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Mnema"
  description="Mnema privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data."
  pathname="/privacy"
>
  <section style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px 120px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 8px;">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 48px;">
      Last updated: May 26, 2026
    </p>

    <div style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75;">

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        1. Data We Collect
      </h2>
      <p>We collect the following categories of information when you use Mnema:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 12px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Account data</strong> — email address, display
          name, and workspace identifiers provided during sign-up.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Content data</strong> — documents, notes, flows,
          and other material you create or import into Mnema.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Usage data</strong> — page views, feature
          interactions, and session metadata used to improve the service.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Payment data</strong> — billing transactions are
          processed by Razorpay; we store only subscription status and plan identifiers, not raw card
          details.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Technical data</strong> — IP address, browser
          type, and error logs collected automatically for security and debugging.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        2. How We Use Your Data
      </h2>
      <p>We use your data to:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 12px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Provide, operate, and maintain the Mnema service.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Authenticate your identity and keep your account secure.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Send transactional emails (magic-link codes, invitations, billing receipts).</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Monitor and improve performance and reliability.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Comply with legal obligations.</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">
        We do not sell your personal data to third parties, and we do not use your content to train
        AI models without your explicit consent.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        3. Data Sharing
      </h2>
      <p>
        We share your data only with the sub-processors required to operate the service:
      </p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 12px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">WorkOS</strong> — authentication provider.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Razorpay</strong> — payment processing.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Resend</strong> — transactional email delivery.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Sentry</strong> — error monitoring (error messages and stack traces only).</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">Vercel / Railway</strong> — hosting and infrastructure.</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">
        All sub-processors are contractually required to handle your data in compliance with applicable
        privacy law.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        4. Data Retention
      </h2>
      <p>
        We retain your account and content data for as long as your account is active. If you cancel
        your account, we retain your data for 30 days before permanent deletion to allow for recovery.
        Anonymised usage statistics may be retained indefinitely.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        5. Your Rights
      </h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to access, correct, export, or delete
        your personal data. To exercise these rights, email us at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:hello@theboringpeople.in" style="color: var(--accent);">hello@theboringpeople.in</a>.
        We will respond within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        6. Cookies
      </h2>
      <p>
        Mnema uses strictly necessary cookies to maintain authentication sessions. We do not use
        third-party tracking or advertising cookies. You can clear cookies at any time through your
        browser settings; doing so will sign you out.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        7. Security
      </h2>
      <p>
        We use industry-standard measures including TLS encryption in transit, encrypted cookies, and
        row-level security in our database to protect your data. No system is 100% secure; in the
        event of a breach affecting your data we will notify you in accordance with applicable law.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        8. Children's Privacy
      </h2>
      <p>
        Mnema is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from
        children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us so we
        can delete it.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        9. Changes to This Policy
      </h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of material changes via
        email or an in-app notice at least 14 days before they take effect.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 40px 0 12px;">
        10. Contact
      </h2>
      <p>
        For privacy enquiries, contact us at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:hello@theboringpeople.in" style="color: var(--accent);">hello@theboringpeople.in</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
